summary: A new preset for Female Imperial characters.
descriptionHtml:
I wanted to make a preset of my old character to re-use it in another game.
I did this for me first but I figured I could share it if someone\'s interested.

It adds an 11th preset for Female Imperial characters. 
Simply start a new game, select the preset during the character creation, change whatever you want and you\'re done.
If you\'re already a female Imperial, type \"showracemenu\" in the console and select the preset.


Here\'s a list of mods I used for my character but none of them are required for the mod to work:

[b]RECOMMENDED MODS (required for the face to look exactly like the one on the screenshot):[/b]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3563] coverwomen look_4 (or seamless UNP and Coverwomen Look_4 if you use UNP body)[/url] by mrLenski
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=7127]RANs type-A Headmesh[/url] by RAN46 
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=3589]Natural Eyes[/url] by nevenbridge
[url=http://www.mediafire.com/?a3z4adv4e3zdrne]TERA HairPack[/url] (haircut)

[b]OTHER MODS (shown in the screenshot):[/b]
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=6709]DIMONIZED UNP female body[/url] by dimon99
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=1040]The Art of Magicka[/url] by Zonzai and Kalell (for the boots)
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=13378]Combination Vanilla Outfit[/url] by sesamin (outfit)
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=14466]Nordguard Follower[/url] by Warvok (handsome follower)
[url=http://skyrim.nexusmods.com/downloads/file.php?id=11954]Pretty Female Idle[/url] by Dualsun (idle pose animation)

Enjoy :)
author: Krag
